    "title": "Urgent Opening Real Estate Agent at Hubtown",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Real Estate Agent looking for your next big career move? Hubtown in Bhubaneswar offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Hubtown:\nHubtown is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Client Relationship Management\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Referral bonus program\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Hubtown!",
